org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.forms.datatypes

Class FormData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.forms.datatypes.FormData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeData, JIPipeValidatable, JIPipeParameterCollection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MaskDrawerFormData, ParameterFormData

    public abstract class FormData
extends Object
implements JIPipeData, JIPipeParameterCollection, JIPipeValidatable
    Base class for any form data. A form data object is a JIPipeParameterCollection and is (de)serialized via the parameter system. Its standard display function shows the user interface with placeholder values
